title: Zeitgeist-GREAT.avi
description: This is an excellent film about the New World Order.  It documents how the government, run from behind the scenes on an international level, has been run in order to slowly take the proceeds of the cash-cow, the american public, and to generate operating capital from it.  From this point it is turned to globalization and world government and controlling any dissident citizen.  This movie goes hand in hand with other documentaries such as the Police State series by Alex Jones, Esoteric Agenda, and many others.  It documents the conspiracy around 9/11, Oliver North, and many other government screw-ups that have given us insight into programs that are normally hidden from the average citizen.  Finally we have enough evidence to see what is really going on here.  It's up to you to decide what to do with it.
